GET
+++

List running testdrives.

Spec: ::

  Accept:
    $CT:testdrives

  Status:
    200 Ok
  Content-Type:
    &Accept

Example: ::

  GET /testdrives
  Accept: $CT:testdrives

  200 Ok
  Content-Type: $CT:testdrives

  [
    {
      "build": "/appliances/123/4.5.6/oem"
